com.shea.tothepathandback

Class MainActivity.StationSortObject

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.shea.tothepathandback.MainActivity.StationSortObject
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Comparable<MainActivity.StationSortObject>
    Enclosing class:
    MainActivity

    public class MainActivity.StationSortObject
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Comparable<MainActivity.StationSortObject>

    An object that each hold a station and the distance or duration from the current location of the user. The purpose for this class is to associate the station with one of those metrics in order to sort through all the stations and to find which is shorter or takes less time to arrive at. Only has get methods, and overridden sort method for two of these objects.
